{"tid":582490,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"鹿兒島火山爆發","createTime":"2018-03-06T08:14:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T14:56:03.000Z","uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bf6a07308668533730f4559c8a6de9f87ffe1db9","tid":582490,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T08:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/161445_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F161445_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=5fabc6ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52f87e65ffb1c1638d9eac38be5928f74d777b17","tid":582490,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T08:15:14.000Z","msg":"日本鹿兒島霧島連山的新燃岳今日發生火山爆發，鹿兒島機場逾60班航班要取消，包括多班香港來往鹿兒島的航班。<br />\n<br />\n氣象廳表示，新燃岳自本月1日起出現連續性的噴發，到當地時間周二下午2時27分左右出現爆發。氣象廳將爆發警戒級別維持在3，並呼籲市民留意距離火山口大約3公里範圍內，會出現大型噴石及火山碎屑流。"},{"pid":"9a9cf2446df3fffd03c87e35e093be662f03d0c7","tid":582490,"uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:36:53.000Z","msg":"等睇閪客<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32619067e1b0d135aca9900c26053df2346e1dd4","tid":582490,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a9cf2446df3fffd03c87e35e093be662f03d0c7","tid":582490,"uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:36:53.000Z","msg":"等睇閪客<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:37:55.000Z","msg":"答我呀 !"},{"pid":"17022f535fb5bf1b5d0f954f2fdbdac6c1e2b54d","tid":582490,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32619067e1b0d135aca9900c26053df2346e1dd4","tid":582490,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a9cf2446df3fffd03c87e35e093